'''''PTXmas''''' 是無伴奏合唱團[[Pentatonix|Pentatonix]]第二張迷你專輯<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/pentatonix-mn0002808236/discography/all|title=Pentatonix - Discography - AllMusic|author=Matt Collar|work=AllMusic|accessdate=October 13, 2014|archive-date=2014-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141027235756/http://www.allmusic.com/artist/pentatonix-mn0002808236/discography/all|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
電子版於2012年11月12日推出，實體版則於2012年11月13日起發售。全碟共收錄了6首翻唱聖誕歌曲，同年11月19日推出的豪華版更額外收錄《[[The_Little_Drummer_Boy|Little Drummer Boy]]》及《Go Tell It On the Mountain》。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ptxofficial.com/news_item&NewsID=3765647615765 |title=PTXMAS DELUXE (WITH 2 NEW TRACKS) - AVAILABLE NOW! |accessdate=December 12, 2013 |archive-date=2018-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180920084222/http://www.ptxofficial.com/news_item%26NewsID%3D3765647615765 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

此專輯共賣出168,000張，是2013年暢銷聖誕專輯的第6位。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/music-news/chart-watch-top-10-christmas-albums-2013-230034592.html|title=Chart Watch|date=January 2, 2014|work=Yahoo Music|accessdate=October 13, 2014|archive-date=2014-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103192902/http://music.yahoo.com/blogs/music-news/chart-watch-top-10-christmas-albums-2013-230034592.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

